{"tid":2507201,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"市傳Facebook最新財報將揭露持有比特幣","createTime":"2021-04-28T00:38:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-28T02:47:54.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5f0140ea44a0c2629c7ae708b9757a1fd1723cdc","tid":2507201,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T00:38:24.000Z","msg":"週二 (27 日) Altana 數位貨幣基金投資長 Alistair Milne 推文爆料，有傳言稱，Facebook 將在發布最新財報時宣布，該公司資產負債表上持有比特幣。<br />\n<br />\n受此消息影響，臉書 (FB-US) 週二小幅上漲 0.17% 至每股 303.57 美元。截稿前，比特幣延續近日漲勢，升逾 2.4% 暫報 5.5 萬美元。<br />\n<br />\n根據在美國加密貨幣生態系統中多個消息來源指出，臉書的資產負債表中包含比特幣。<br />\n<br />\nAltana 數位貨幣基金投資長 Alistair Milne 週二爆料，臉書將於 28 日公布最新財報時披露持有比特幣。<br />\n<br />\n梅薩里 (Messari) 研究分析師 Mira Christanto 週二表示，近期比特幣價格波動都來自巨頭的買入和賣出的動作。<br />\n<br />\nMira Christanto 提到，近期比特幣價格跌至 48,000 美元以下是由於特斯拉 (TSLA-US) 出售 10% 持有的比特幣，而近日比特幣反彈是由於臉書購買了比特幣。<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.cnyes.com/news/id/4634626\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.cnyes.com%2Fnews%2Fid%2F4634626&d=APk9rvMsCVL9feuIhYiW0gbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=6148d16d\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.cnyes.com/news/id/4634626</a>"},{"pid":"0865c91c96b900763a3ee17e87c103ff1ebec5f8","tid":2507201,"uid":360041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T00:41:29.000Z","msg":"Keyword: 多個消息，將發表，持有比特幣"},{"pid":"3416f09f30a615ed3d900b62fa197a43140e5984","tid":2507201,"uid":120955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T00:57:14.000Z","msg":"tsla 買coin 股價跌<br />\nfb 買coin 股價升<br />\n根本就無撚關係"},{"pid":"df43bd32d0f67445d74f7c2e0e8010ff7dd6f656","tid":2507201,"uid":101328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T01:09:38.000Z","msg":"Facebook自己都想出幣啦"},{"pid":"1e71925071e783879964b400541ef589c5289c34","tid":2507201,"uid":14867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T01:20:07.000Z","msg":"傻仔：scam <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><im